    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Adult patients (age &gt;20 y/o)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  ICU admission for acute respiratory failure due to community-acquired pneumonia by&#xD;
             clinical diagnosis&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Treatment with endotracheal Intubation&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Aspiration pneumonia (including witnessed aspiration and chronic bedridden status)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Nosocomial infection&#xD;
      </textblock>
